text: Mohammed al-Khamis ben Yusef ben Hassan al-Alawi (), also known as Sidi Mohammed ben Yusef () or Mohammed V () (10 August 1909 â€“ 26 February 1961), was Sultan of Morocco from 1927 to 1953.
